    Load assessments from a package/directory

    MakeAssessmentList.Rd

    Load assessments from a package/directory

    MakeAssessmentList(path = "assessments", package = "gsm")

    Arguments

    path

    location of assessment yaml files. If package is specified looks in /inst folder.

    package

    package with assessments

    Value

    A list of assessments

    Details

    Coming soon

    Examples

     MakeAssessmentList(path="assessments", package="gsm")
